snippet badge-license "badge for license"
[![license][license-badge]][license]
[license]: LICENSE
[license-badge]: https://img.shields.io/github/license/${1:owner}/${2:repo}?style=for-the-badge
endsnippet

snippet badge-release "badge for github release"
[![release][release-badge]][release]
[release]: https://github.com/${1:owner}/${2:repo}/releases
[release-badge]: https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/$1/$2?style=for-the-badge&logo=github
endsnippet

snippet badge-actions-workflow "badge for github actions workflow"
[![actions-workflow-${1:Test}][actions-workflow-$1-badge]][actions-workflow-$1]
[actions-workflow-$1]: https://github.com/${2:owner}/${3:repo}/actions?query=workflow%3A$1
[actions-workflow-$1-badge]: https://img.shields.io/github/workflow/status/$2/$3/$1?label=$1&style=for-the-badge&logo=github
endsnippet

snippet badge-actions-marketplace "badge for github actions marketplace"
[![actions-marketplace][actions-marketplace-badge]][actions-marketplace]
[actions-marketplace]: https://github.com/marketplace/actions/${1:action}
[actions-marketplace-badge]: https://img.shields.io/badge/marketplace-${2:display-name}-blue?style=for-the-badge&logo=github
endsnippet

snippet badge-codecov "badge for codecov"
